data.name: Greeting
data.value:
Hello, my name is Ba Cing,
I will be your assistant in the Merchant Master game. I will inform you about the current and upcoming rankings and events, the appearance of the Great Ape Siege or Mountain Adventure, as well as the update of the assortment in the Banquet Shop. I will also tell you when the stores on Shopper Row have been updated.
You can find out about all my options with the command /help

data.value: I am at your service, how can I help you? You can contact me for the following commands:

data.name: TextBanquetShop
data.value: 🛍In the Banquet Shop the assortment of goods has been updated. Check what's new. And don't forget to buy hammers to build your guild.

data.name: TextMessageGAS
data.value: 🐵The Siege of the Great Ape has begun! Don't forget to switch the main spirit between talents for efficient damage.

data.name: TextMessageMA
data.value: 🐨The Mountain Adventure has begun! Do not forget to calculate the damage you need to inflict.

data.value: 🥇The following ratings will start next: 💪'Battle of Talents' During this ranking, you need to maximize the power of your talents. Do not forget to arrange with other guild members for help.

data.name: textRankingNext1
data.value: 🥇The following ratings will start next: 💜'Duel of Intimacy' In this rating, you need to increase the intimacy of loved ones with the help of gifts and costumes. data.name: textRankingNext2
